TextChange: There is a small movement of people who are trying to focus on experiences instead of presents for children over their birthdays. I love this movement and want to try and implement it with my daughter as she grows up! The memories from experiences like going to the aquarium or zoo will be more fufilling to our relationship than if I buy her 5 toys for her birthday.
